{
  "id": "RAW_fc5287",
  "title": "Manus 爆火的背后，Agentic AI 产品如何构筑持久的竞争优势？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/xIvReVX4cyRrUSV07JNKOQ",
  "date": "2025-03-20 03:23:54",
  "author": "鸭哥",
  "siteName": "十字路口Crossing",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"margin:0px 0px 20px;border-right:1px dashed rgb(34, 34, 34);white-space:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;line-height:26px;border-bottom:1px dashed rgb(34, 34, 34);\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;font-size: 15px;\">\n     <section style=\"width: 90%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0px 0px 10px;border-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-size: 15px;\">\n      <section style=\"margin-top: 10px;font-size: 15px;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🚥&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Koji 按:</span>&nbsp;下周，十字路口的播客是「20 问」专栏第三期。我们打算在 Manus 爆火三周后，用 20 个问题聊清楚 AI Agent 这个 2025 年最热门的话题之一。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本期的嘉宾之一是这篇文章的作者鸭哥。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">欢迎大家在小宇宙和 Apple Podcast 订阅「十字路口」播客，收听我们下周的节目。</span></p>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;min-height: 20px;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/58dc95e3-d181-4a14-5505-3a0fff802a00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/FFcNSoQ3KicuDDLm99KH74p7QpOicghtfND09b6TLl4OFhtkicaOx6fu7jVPQPQwvNeJibgR9ZoVI5IqjNAIU0F8UA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"289\" data-imgfileid=\"501607441\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/58dc95e3-d181-4a14-5505-3a0fff802a00/public\"></span></p>\n   <section style=\"margin:20px 0px;border-right:1px dashed rgb(34, 34, 34);white-space:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;line-height:26px;border-bottom:1px dashed rgb(34, 34, 34);\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;font-size: 15px;\">\n     <section style=\"width: 90%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0px 0px 10px;border-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-size: 15px;\">\n      <section style=\"margin-top: 10px;font-size: 15px;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">🚥 作者 &nbsp;Yan Wang / 鸭哥</span></span></p>\n      </section><span leaf=\"\">Samsara 应用科学家，哥伦比亚大学博士，曾在 Pinterest / Microsoft 等公司工作，发表过近40篇国际顶会期刊论文。个人网站：</span><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Computing Life</span><sup style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">[1]</span></sup></strong>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;min-height: 20px;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">最近，Manus发布并迅速火遍了中文互联网。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">在深度使用了Manus以后，我觉得这个产品确实充满了启发。它抓住了Agentic AI产品竞争中非常重要的一方面，也就是复利效应。这篇文章就想聊一聊，对于类似Deep Research、Cursor或者Manus这样的Agentic AI产品，从更长时间的尺度来看，</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">竞争的要点在哪些方面，以及哪些因素可以构成有效的护城河，哪些因素不可以。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;min-height: 20px;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ca109d45-a2a4-4d46-8a77-5802e9b99d00/public\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"501607437\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ca109d45-a2a4-4d46-8a77-5802e9b99d00/public\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;min-height: 20px;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在具体介绍Agentic AI产品竞争的三个重要方面之前，我想先解释一下</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么我觉得Manus是一个很惊艳的产品。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">其实，和很多自媒体渲染的情况不同，Manus不是一个石破天惊、从石头缝里蹦出来的产品，或者在它之前就没有任何人尝试过类似的产品形式。相反，它的出现是有着明确的发展脉络的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">和它最相关的两种产品形式：</span></p>\n   <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;padding-left: 1.5em;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin-bottom: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;list-style-position: outside;\">\n     <p style=\"border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 15px;line-height: inherit;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;margin: 10px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个是Agentic调研类产品，比如Gemini、Perplexity和OpenAI的Deep Research。他们可以让你输入一个简单的主题或者要求，接着帮你调研全网的数据，并且生成一个详实且有深度的报告。</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;list-style-position: outside;\">\n     <p style=\"border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 15px;line-height: inherit;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;margin: 10px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">另一种相关的形式是Cursor、Devin或者Gamma之类的Agentic生成类产品。你给它一个要求，它可以帮你写作代码、文稿或者幻灯片，直接交付你想要的产出形式。</span></p></li>\n   </ol>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在2024年，这两种类型的产品都有了长足的发展，并且跨过了可用性的门坎，出现了病毒式的爆发增长。</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;margin:20px 0px;border-right:none;display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;border-bottom:none;word-spacing:normal;outline:0px;overflow:auto;border-left:8px solid rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;hyphens:auto;text-align:left;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但是，还有一大痛点是：我要不然只能做调研，要不然只能写代码。二者之间并没有有效打通。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这其实是个非常微妙的痛点，因为Agentic AI好用的根本原因就在于，它通过自我迭代、自主决策，就可以帮我们一站式地完成复杂的任务。但如果我们在实际工作中还要不停地思考，这件事要用OpenAI的Deep Research来做，然后把结果复制粘贴到Cursor里面生成一些可视化的图像，最后再把这二者合并在一起，扔给Gamma去生成PPT，这其实完全和Agentic AI的初衷背道而驰，也丧失了使用Agentic AI的意义。</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;margin:20px 0px;border-right:none;display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;border-bottom:none;word-spacing:normal;outline:0px;overflow:auto;border-left:8px solid rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;hyphens:auto;text-align:left;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Manus让人觉得惊艳的地方就在于它打通了整条链路。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一方面，它可以以Agentic的形式进行调研，通过浏览互联网来收集全面详实的资料。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">另一方面，它也可以根据这些资料，进行更多的分析、可视化，从而生成最终的产出，比如网站、图文报告或者幻灯片。这种端到端的应用场景在以往的产品中都是很难实现的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">再加上，Manus本身产品特性打磨得也很好，完整度很高。作为一个思路精准又好用的产品，自然就引发了爆款。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:40px auto;font-weight:bold;width:fit-content;font-size:20px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">工具的复利</span></h2>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4c9f6092-162e-4010-286a-0852a1841e00/public\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"501607436\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4c9f6092-162e-4010-286a-0852a1841e00/public\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但是，上面的这些观察其实并没有触及到Agentic AI中更本质的特点，或者说优势。</span></span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;margin:20px 0px;border-right:none;display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;border-bottom:none;word-spacing:normal;outline:0px;overflow:auto;border-left:8px solid rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;hyphens:auto;text-align:left;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在我看来，Agentic AI相比于传统AI，一个鲜明的特征是它在多个维度上都具有复利效应（Compound Effect）。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在Manus的例子里，它为什么能取得成功，一个重要的原因是：</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它能使用的工具的数量比以往的产品都要多。这其实是一个并不trivial的区别。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在Agentic AI产品中，能使用的工具的数量从6个到8个所带来的产品体验变化，要远远大于从2个到4个所带来的变化。这是因为AI所使用的工具之间是可以相互组合、相互促进的。如果一个AI只会写代码和搜索文本，这时候给它加一个图像搜索的功能，或许不会有太多的好处。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但如果它在这个基础上还能写报告、做PPT，这个时候加入图像搜索的能力，就会一下让它产出的报告和幻灯片变得多彩很多，从而有力地推动了产品体验。</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;margin:20px 0px;border-right:none;display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;border-bottom:none;word-spacing:normal;outline:0px;overflow:auto;border-left:8px solid rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;hyphens:auto;text-align:left;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而这恰恰是Manus干的事情。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">即使不论它做的其他创新，即使我们只看它把Deep Research和Cursor这两种产品并在一起，这个单纯的工具数量的增长，立刻就让它完成了很多以前的产品实现不了的场景。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就是Agentic AI的第一种复利效应。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">当我们增加它能调用的工具的数量的时候，它带来的好处是组合的、爆炸式的增长。这是一种非常现实的增强用户体验的手段，但是它并不能构建一条有效的护城河。原因是在现在 Cursor 等等工具的支持下，单纯地对接某种工具让 AI 能够自主调用是一件非常简单的事情。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果抛开产品力不谈，只是想复刻一个 Manus 的话，这件事本身并不难。而单纯地通过卷工具的数量来构建护城河，也不是一个长久之计。</span></span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:40px auto;font-weight:bold;width:fit-content;font-size:20px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">数据的复利</span></h2>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5fcf8f76-838a-43a8-8f30-9799442d2c00/public\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"501607438\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5fcf8f76-838a-43a8-8f30-9799442d2c00/public\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而其实Agentic AI 在其他方面也有类似的复利效应。</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;margin:20px 0px;border-right:none;display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;border-bottom:none;word-spacing:normal;outline:0px;overflow:auto;border-left:8px solid rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;hyphens:auto;text-align:left;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个被很多人忽视的方面是数据。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里的数据指的不是类似LLM预训练的数据。你用了2T Token，我用了3T Token，我就比你厉害。在Agentic AI的时代，它有着更深刻的含义。确切地说，这里的数据指的不是数据量本身，而是横贯整个生命周期的数据的获取、组织和外化。在和人类共事的过程中，我们往往会体会到“家有一老，如有一宝”。比如工厂里一个机器坏了，老员工过来就知道在哪里拍一拍就可以把它弄好。或者有经验的医生看病的时候，随便摸两下就能把病因说得八九不离十。但是，刚毕业的小年轻往往要做很多检查项目才能约略得到类似的结论。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就是一个典型的数据带来的好处。</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于人而言，在这个过程中主要发生了两件事情</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：第一是经验的积累，无论是机械厂的员工还是医生，在他几十年的从业生涯中都遇到过很多类似的故障或者病例。在这个基础上，他就可以再进行第二步，总结归纳，也就是知识的组织。到了这一步，这些知识就被内化到他们的记忆里，对人类而言已经够用了。但是，由于AI与人类的沟通目前还完全依赖于书面沟通，所以往往还需要一个知识外化的过程，将它沉淀成一个明确的文档，才能被AI所使用。</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;margin:20px 0px;border-right:none;display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;border-bottom:none;word-spacing:normal;outline:0px;overflow:auto;border-left:8px solid rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;hyphens:auto;text-align:left;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">因此，对于Agentic AI来说，维持一个知识积累、组织和外化的循环是非常重要的。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个我们之前提到过的软件工程的例子是，如果有一个写代码的AI，你直接给它一个十万行的代码仓库，并且给它布置一些任务，它一步成功就完成所有任务的概率其实不大。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但如果你给它一些时间，让它逐渐阅读代码，并且加以理解、消化和分类，在这个基础上把它学到的东西总结、沉淀成一个个的文档，此时它的编码工作就会简单很多。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里</span><sup style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">[2]</span></sup></strong><span leaf=\"\">是一个这种文档的例子。在里面，我们介绍了代码的基本架构、设计思想、不同的函数放在哪些文件里。对于历史比较久的项目，我们还可以再加上一些历史的context。有了这些文档的支撑以后，一方面在空间上，AI就知道如何精准地定位要更改的代码，而不会无脑地去新建一个文件，把所有东西都从头写。从时间的维度上，AI也会知道之前做过哪些尝试，当前的设计思路是什么，而不会陷入鬼打墙，把设计方案又改回了以前的状态。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">因此，在这里我们所说的数据不是单纯的数据的堆砌、Token的叠加，而是一个长期的，自动或半自动化积累、理解和沉淀的过程。对于一个固定的客户来说，AI和他共事的时间越长，就可以积累越多的类似的知识。相比于另一个初来乍到、没有任何背景的AI，哪怕后者的智能程度更高，用户也会觉得前一个AI使用起来更舒服，它更懂我。因此这种知识系统的二次处理，是一个有效的护城河。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而类似的，这种数据的积累也有组合的复利效应。有更多的历史数据和总结出来的文档，AI就能通过对比和思考，形成更多的洞察。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从某种程度上来说，这是一个把传统的知识系统变成一个AI友好（AI Friendly）的知识系统的过程。</span></span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;margin:20px 0px;border-right:none;display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;border-bottom:none;word-spacing:normal;outline:0px;overflow:auto;border-left:8px solid rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;hyphens:auto;text-align:left;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI friendly不是一个非黑即白的二元状态，而是一个需要时间去沉淀和发展的东西。我甚至愿意把它和人与自然的共同进化（co-evolution）来类比。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一方面，AI会从原始的知识库中进行挖掘、提炼和积累。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">另一方面，用户在使用AI的过程中也会越来越体会到，如果我们把各种数据让AI能轻松获取，对自己的工作而言也大有裨益。因此，他们就更愿意改变自己的工作方式来适应AI的数据管理流程。这又会带来额外的好处，比如以前在Zoom会议里面丧失的tribal knowledge，如果用户愿意引入Zoom AI Companion，那这些知识就会被捕捉下来，并且沉淀到文档库里，为AI所用来帮助用户。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就形成了一个双向奔赴的正向循环。而这个彼此的适应和默契，是一个非常强的护城河。</span></span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:40px auto;font-weight:bold;width:fit-content;font-size:20px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">智能的复利</span></h2>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c5a5bf8a-80f5-44e4-0d8f-6d763de65100/public\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"501607435\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c5a5bf8a-80f5-44e4-0d8f-6d763de65100/public\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agentic AI还有一个非常有意思的特点，就是</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">智能本身也是有复利的。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">这件事情可能不像工具和数据那么容易理解。但是，一个工具的智能程度会从多个角度对Agentic的用户体验带来影响。</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;margin:20px 0px;border-right:none;display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;border-bottom:none;word-spacing:normal;outline:0px;overflow:auto;border-left:8px solid rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;hyphens:auto;text-align:left;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">最粗浅的角度是，越聪明的工具，它越知道怎么样去高效理解用户的需求，也知道怎么组合少数几个工具来获得最大的收益。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如，一个没那么智能的LLM，可能会东一榔头西一棒，调用了很多工具之后，还是没办法得到足够的信息。但是，会思考的LLM看起来就更有章法。通过巧妙地组合少数的几种工具，就可以在短时间内解决问题。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">另一个相关的因素是，</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你对比过Gemini和OpenAI的Deep Research，就会发现这两个AI段位完全不一样。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini更像是机械地follow一个事先定好的指令，先想一些关键字上网搜索，然后自主决定抓取哪些网页，最后基于这些网页内容进行汇总回答。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但OpenAI的Deep Research就会感觉更主动，自我迭代的能力也更强。它会先制定一个计划，然后根据计划用不同的关键字进行搜索。在搜索的过程中，根据结果它还可能动态调整策略。最终生成的答案往往也富有启发，不仅回答问题本身，还会自主延伸出下一步可能有价值的研究方向。</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种自主性所带来的增益也是非线性的。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">考虑到现在有能力进行自主LLM研发的公司并不多，同时，LLM的训练是一个非常强调资源和资本的事情。因此，这一定程度上也是一个</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">有意义的护城河。</span></span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:40px auto;font-weight:bold;width:fit-content;font-size:20px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">竞争的要点</span></h2>\n   <blockquote style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;margin:20px 0px;border-right:none;display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;border-bottom:none;word-spacing:normal;outline:0px;overflow:auto;border-left:8px solid rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;hyphens:auto;text-align:left;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过我想强调的一点是，这三种复利并不是平行的加法关系，而是有彼此激发和影响的乘数效应。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">工具数量的增多会为信息的处理和积累提供更多出口，比如在项目管理、搜索、文档生成等多个维度留下可以供 AI 学习的数据接口。AI 在分析这些信息的时候，也在不断提升自己的推理和理解能力。这种协同演化的效果在 Manus 中就非常明显。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">起初，Deep Research 能够做深入调研，Cursor 能够写代码、写文档，但一旦把二者融合在一个 Agentic 平台上，AI 就可以对调研得到的信息进行进一步的逻辑加工、编排和发布。</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;margin:20px 0px;border-right:none;display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;border-bottom:none;word-spacing:normal;outline:0px;overflow:auto;border-left:8px solid rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;hyphens:auto;text-align:left;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而这些信息、工具和智能在同一个闭环中相互刺激，就给用户带来了一种更流畅、更智能的全流程体验。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">因此，</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agentic AI 竞争的重点可能就在于如何尽早地扩展到工具、数据或者智能这些指数增长曲线的右侧。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">这是因为花费同样的精力来增长工具的数量或者数据的数量，在初期得到的收益是相对有限的。但是，当它跨越一个 tipping point 以后，指数增长的威力就会显现出来。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在曲线的右侧，每增加一个工具、增加一点数据，就会让用户的体验顺畅很多。因此，这可能是 Agentic AI 相关产品开展竞争、构建护城河的关键。当然，这条指数曲线并不一定会无限延伸下去，而可能是一个 S 形。到达某个节点以后，再继续加入新工具或者新信息，就会受到系统复杂度与资源投入的掣肘，导致增长减缓，甚至可能在某些阶段出现瓶颈。此时，可能就需要在架构和协作机制上做更深层的创新，来保持系统的协同演化。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而从上面的讨论也可以看出，在工具方面建立护城河不是特别可靠。</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从LLM智能方面建立护城河需要大量的资源，而从数据方面建立护城河可能是最简便可行的一种方法。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在数据沉淀之外，可能更重要的是如何进行沉淀的流程与方法论。因为数据本身是可以复制的，但是如何系统性地将隐性知识外化，如何进行结构化沉淀以及高效数据管理，这是极其难以复制的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这类似于企业文化，一旦形成了强大的数据管理与知识外化的方法论和流程体系，即使竞争对手把这些数据和工具都复制过去，也很难在短期内复制这种隐性的组织能力。</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;margin:20px 0px;border-right:none;display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;border-bottom:none;word-spacing:normal;outline:0px;overflow:auto;border-left:8px solid rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;hyphens:auto;text-align:left;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">因此，在Agentic AI产品的长期竞争中，最难以攻破的不是数据或者智能的规模，而是这种数据与工具使用的体系化组织能力。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:40px auto;font-weight:bold;width:fit-content;font-size:20px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">小结</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从Manus出发，我们看到了Agentic AI领域竞争的关键点与护城河所在。</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;margin:20px 0px;border-right:none;display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;border-bottom:none;word-spacing:normal;outline:0px;overflow:auto;border-left:8px solid rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;hyphens:auto;text-align:left;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但更重要的是，这场竞争并不仅仅是关于工具数量的比拼或数据规模的较量，而是组织如何适应AI时代的深刻转型。未来胜出的可能并不是拥有最强技术的公司，而是那些真正理解了AI与人类如何共进化、并能建立持续、稳定的协作机制的公司。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这也许才是Agentic AI真正为我们带来的启示。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;min-height: 20px;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0px 0px;border-color: rgb(121, 121, 121);transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);font-size: 15px;\">\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;min-height: 20px;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">ps，在文章的末尾，向大家安利鸭哥的 AI 课程&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">《FROM USERS TO BUILDERS - 完成自我进化，拥抱AI时代》</span><sup style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">[3]</span></sup></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;，欢迎感兴趣的朋友们了解。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2282a42c-e8b5-4711-3cdd-5a0b4d7ea800/public\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.24351851851851852\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"501607434\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2282a42c-e8b5-4711-3cdd-5a0b4d7ea800/public\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d83a901d-0aae-45ca-0992-01c538e70000/public\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"501607439\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d83a901d-0aae-45ca-0992-01c538e70000/public\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/af5dfcca-247a-4c97-3b55-3597c0ed7700/public\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;font-size: 15px;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"501607440\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/af5dfcca-247a-4c97-3b55-3597c0ed7700/public\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <h3 style=\"margin:40px 0px;font-weight:bold;width:fit-content;font-size:17px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料</span></h3>\n   <section style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <span style=\"display: flex;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"display: inline;margin-right: 4px;background-image: none;background-position: initial;background-size: initial;background-repeat: initial;background-attachment: initial;background-origin: initial;background-clip: initial;font-size: 15px;opacity: 0.6;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">[1]</span></span>\n      <p style=\"display: inline;font-size: 15px;width: 90%;line-height: 26px;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">Computing Life:&nbsp;</span><em style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://yage.ai/</span></em></p></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <span style=\"display: flex;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"display: inline;margin-right: 4px;background-image: none;background-position: initial;background-size: initial;background-repeat: initial;background-attachment: initial;background-origin: initial;background-clip: initial;font-size: 15px;opacity: 0.6;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">[2]</span></span>\n      <p style=\"display: inline;font-size: 15px;width: 90%;line-height: 26px;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里:&nbsp;</span><em style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://github.com/grapeot/web_agentic_ai/blob/master/claude-tooling/app/README.md</span></em></p></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <span style=\"display: flex;font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"display: inline;margin-right: 4px;background-image: none;background-position: initial;background-size: initial;background-repeat: initial;background-attachment: initial;background-origin: initial;background-clip: initial;font-size: 15px;opacity: 0.6;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">[3]</span></span>\n      <p style=\"display: inline;font-size: 15px;width: 90%;line-height: 26px;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">《FROM USERS TO BUILDERS - 完成自我进化，拥抱AI时代》:&nbsp;</span><em style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://www.superlinear.academy/c/ai/</span></em></p></span>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Agentic AI 产品 Manus 通过工具、数据和智能的复利效应构建竞争优势，其中数据和工具的体系化组织能力至关重要。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Agentic AI 产品 Manus 通过工具、数据和智能的复利效应构建竞争优势，其中数据和工具的体系化组织能力至关重要。",
  "summary": "文章深入分析了 Agentic AI 产品 Manus 爆火的原因，认为其成功在于打通了调研和生成链路，实现了端到端的应用场景。文章进一步探讨了 Agentic AI 产品竞争的关键要素，指出工具、数据和智能都具有复利效应，能够带来组合式、爆炸式的增长。其中，数据的复利效应体现在知识的积累、组织和外化，能够形成 AI 友好的知识系统。智能的复利效应则体现在 AI 能够更高效地理解用户需求，并自主调整策略。文章强调，Agentic AI 竞争的重点在于尽早扩展到工具、数据或智能的指数增长曲线右侧，建立持续、稳定的协作机制，实现 AI 与人类的共进化，而**数据和工具使用的体系化组织能力是在 Agentic AI 产品的长期竞争中最难以攻破的壁垒**。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
